Package nfts

Class Nft2D

java.lang.Object
nfts.Nft2D
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, NFT
Direct Known Subclasses:
Nft3D
public class Nft2D extends Object implements NFT, Serializable
The Nft2D class represent one basic type of NFT. This type is important, because it implements all needed functions with product to this class and all classes, which extends this class. PRoduct contains Account representing name of owner of specific product. Also basic important information name, setName, rarity and price are needed.
